00:13:20,410 --> 00:13:24,144
der shver, dem man's tate, hot gehat a ferd

210
00:13:24,144 --> 00:13:26,844
mit a vogn. hot men aroyfgezetst

211
00:13:26,844 --> 00:13:28,483
di kinder

212
00:13:28,483 --> 00:13:30,469
oyfn ferd mitn vogn,

213
00:13:30,469 --> 00:13:32,818
oyfn vogn, un zey zaynen gegan PESHKOM,

214
00:13:32,818 --> 00:13:36,295
un zaynen avekgeforn oyf Yaneve. vos hobn zey gemeynt?

215
00:13:36,295 --> 00:13:41,294
az in Yaneve vet dortn zayn shtil, un di daytshn veln nit kumen.

216
00:13:41,419 --> 00:13:46,475
hobn zey gehat a toes. di daytshn zaynen shoyn ongekumen zey antkegn.

217
00:13:47,292 --> 00:13:50,745
di bombes iz gefloygn ibern kop.

218
00:13:50,970 --> 00:13:58,051
zey zaynen zikh arop dortn in a groysn keler bahaltn. in keler zaynen arayn tsvey hundert mentshn.

219
00:13:59,003 --> 00:14:05,780
nor s'hot getrofn a bombe oyf dem moyer, un in keler zaynen ale dershtikt gevorn.

220
00:14:05,871 --> 00:14:10,455
dortn iz geven di shvester mitn man mit tsvey kinder.

221
00:14:11,153 --> 00:14:13,374
zaynen ale dershtikt gevorn.

222
00:14:15,692 --> 00:14:17,536
oy, ⟨mame⟩.

223
00:14:17,700 --> 00:14:22,672
nu, ot hot men undz avekgeshikt in Shantser lager. dortn iz geven di aktsye,

224
00:14:23,269 --> 00:14:25,153
hot men tsugenumen

225
00:14:25,176 --> 00:14:28,140
mayn meydele. zi iz shoyn geven

226
00:14:28,737 --> 00:14:32,139
dray yor mit dray a halb monat.

227
00:14:34,828 --> 00:14:35,845
oy.

228
00:14:36,752 --> 00:14:40,342
nu, in nokh a bisl tsayt arum hot men

229
00:14:40,342 --> 00:14:43,243
aroysgefirt undz in Shtuthof,

230
00:14:44,110 --> 00:14:45,644
dem gantsn lager.

231
00:14:45,631 --> 00:14:49,100
ver iz geven mit aykh fun ayer mishpokhe?

232
00:14:50,657 --> 00:14:55,139
mit mir iz nor geven der man, di mame,

233
00:14:55,483 --> 00:14:57,013
mer keyner nit.

234
00:14:58,321 --> 00:15:02,301
vu iz geven ayer foter? di yingere shvesterl?

235
00:15:02,331 --> 00:15:06,260
o, dos iz shpeter. zey zaynen geven in geto.

236
00:15:06,486 --> 00:15:08,624
s'iz geven a aktsye...

237
00:15:08,624 --> 00:15:12,183
dos iz geven di letste aktsye... oyf zeyer gas,

238
00:15:12,679 --> 00:15:16,385
zaynen zey avek oyf di aktsye, oykh oyfn nayntn fort.

239
00:15:19,597 --> 00:15:23,147
vos hot ir gegesn in Shantser lager?

240
00:15:24,209 --> 00:15:25,612
vos hot men gegesn?

241
00:15:25,503 --> 00:15:26,317
ye.

242
00:15:26,429 --> 00:15:29,076
ay, vos iz geven?

243
00:15:29,892 --> 00:15:32,805
vos hot men gegesn? vi eyner hot gehat,

244
00:15:32,895 --> 00:15:35,046
vos eyner hot fardint,

245
00:15:35,046 --> 00:15:37,563
hot er zikh gekoyft un gegesn.

246
00:15:39,595 --> 00:15:44,999
nu, ikh'l dertseyln ⟨nakher v-⟩ vi m'hot avekgefirt undz ⟨nakher⟩,

247
00:15:44,999 --> 00:15:47,959
hot men RESHAet undz aroysfirn in Shtuthof.

248
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:53,814
iz geshtanen oyfn, vokzal vagones,

249
00:15:55,002 --> 00:15:56,751
un me hot undz

250
00:15:57,600 --> 00:15:59,956
getribn tsu di vagones.

251
00:16:00,773 --> 00:16:03,635
az s'iz gevorn ful ale vagones,

252
00:16:04,452 --> 00:16:07,662
iz der poyezd hot ongehoybn forn.

253
00:16:10,898 --> 00:16:13,744
m'hot undz avekgefirt in Shtuthof.

254
00:16:13,783 --> 00:16:15,948
in Shtuthof,

255
00:16:15,948 --> 00:16:18,561
dortn iz geven eyner,

256
00:16:18,846 --> 00:16:21,381
a polyak, KAWKI.

257
00:16:21,381 --> 00:16:23,987
er iz geven aza shlekhter.

258
00:16:24,128 --> 00:16:27,775
s'iz geven a shrek. er hot alemen geharget.

259
00:16:29,646 --> 00:16:32,393
nit geven far vos er hot geharget.

260
00:16:32,393 --> 00:16:35,793
m'hot dortn gegebn zup in shiselekh.

261
00:16:35,793 --> 00:16:42,836
hot yeder eyner gedarft oyfesn di zup un opgebn a leydike shisele, az di iberike zoln kenen esn.

262
00:16:42,893 --> 00:16:46,180
ober az s'iz geven nit meglekh tsum esn,

263
00:16:46,180 --> 00:16:49,142
hot men avekgeshtelt di shisele mit di esn.

264
00:16:49,142 --> 00:16:52,708
hot er dos gegosn oyfn kop, in di oygn,

265
00:16:52,798 --> 00:16:55,981
un er hot geharget, me zol oyfesn di zup.

266
00:16:56,157 --> 00:17:01,714
nakher hobn shoyn ale moyre gehat, hot men ongehoybn shoyn esn di zup, far moyre.

267
00:17:01,714 --> 00:17:04,011
er flegt hargenen a shrek.

268
00:17:04,358 --> 00:17:09,566
flegt zayn an apel, flegt men darfn oysshteyn. er flegt tseyln, er flegt

269
00:17:09,656 --> 00:17:11,590
proste mutshenen.

270
00:17:12,222 --> 00:17:15,186
flegt men darfn oysshteyn shoen.

271
00:17:16,676 --> 00:17:23,926
ikh bin geshtanen oyfn apel un di zun hot gebrent. s'iz geven azoy heys, kh'hob geshpirt, ikh khalesh avek. ikh loz zikh arop.

272
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:27,279
hob ikh gezogt tsu di, shokhnte mayne,

273
00:17:27,279 --> 00:17:31,469
"ikh ken nit oysshteyn. ikh loz zikh arop." zogt zi, "neyn.

274
00:17:31,469 --> 00:17:33,629
halt zikh; er vet dir avekhargenen.

275
00:17:33,771 --> 00:17:35,615
halt zikh. shtey.

276
00:17:35,615 --> 00:17:36,565
halt zikh."

277
00:17:36,758 --> 00:17:39,654
mit di letste koykhes fleg ikh oysshteyn.

278
00:17:40,285 --> 00:17:42,371
shoen flegt er ophaltn.

279
00:17:43,693 --> 00:17:46,775
⟨nakher⟩ hot zikh gehat a privitshke:

280
00:17:46,832 --> 00:17:53,744
er flegt... me zitst in lager, shoyn oyf dr'erd oysgezetst. s'iz dokh nit geven oyf vos tsum zits-

281
00:17:53,744 --> 00:17:55,275
oyf dr'erd.

282
00:17:55,275 --> 00:17:59,060
un eyne a froy iz geven zeyer a gelernte, a ongeleyente.

283
00:17:59,134 --> 00:18:00,967
 flegt zi leyenen,

284
00:18:01,581 --> 00:18:05,787
di bikher vos zi hot oysgeleyent flegt zi leyenen far undz,

285
00:18:05,787 --> 00:18:08,171
az s'zol zayn PRIATNer.

286
00:18:08,171 --> 00:18:10,262
 un mir flegn zitsn un her⟨n⟩.

287
00:18:10,262 --> 00:18:12,392
mit eyn mol flegt er arayngeyn:

288
00:18:13,512 --> 00:18:16,239
aroys fun lager, aroystraybn.

289
00:18:17,106 --> 00:18:18,298
avu?

290
00:18:18,642 --> 00:18:21,690
ale geyen shoyn aroys, er traybt oyf tsurik.

291
00:18:24,177 --> 00:18:25,886
er iz geven a sadist.

292
00:18:25,886 --> 00:18:28,544
flegt er m- veln mutshenen.

293
00:18:28,544 --> 00:18:32,343
flegt er traybn ahin, oyf tsurik, ahin, oyf tsurik,

294
00:18:32,343 --> 00:18:34,127
zikh izdyekeven.

295
00:18:36,158 --> 00:18:39,780
nu, s'iz geven nit lang der lebn. s'hot geklekt.

296
00:18:40,232 --> 00:18:47,157
 nakher... lang hot men undz nit gehaltn in Shtuthof: tsvey vokhn. un nakher hot men undz avekgeshikt oyf der arbet.

297
00:18:47,157 --> 00:18:50,496
vu iz geven di arbet? grobn

298
00:18:51,396 --> 00:18:52,549
kanaln.

299
00:18:52,549 --> 00:18:55,544
dos iz, "akopes" hobn zey dos ongerufn.

300
00:18:55,544 --> 00:18:57,215
dos hobn di daytshn

301
00:18:58,399 --> 00:19:05,111
tsugegreyt far zikh. v- oybe di rusn veln kumen in shtot, veln zey durkh di kanaln

302
00:19:05,111 --> 00:19:07,910
durkhloyfn un antloyfn.

303
00:19:08,119 --> 00:19:10,434
nor zey hobn a toes gehat:

304
00:19:10,434 --> 00:19:15,015
IMENNO durkh di kanaln zaynen ongekumen di rusn,

305
00:19:15,358 --> 00:19:22,147
un di daytshn hobn afile nit bamerkt vi di shtot iz gevorn ful mit di rusishe armeyen,

306
00:19:22,147 --> 00:19:25,038
vayl zey zaynen durkh durkh di kanaln.

307
00:19:27,424 --> 00:19:33,715
nu, dan hot shoyn gezogt, der daytsh, der onfirer fun lager,

308
00:19:33,715 --> 00:19:38,471
az er hot a bafel, mir zoln aroysf- aroysmarshirn.

309
00:19:38,612 --> 00:19:44,428
mir, ale lagern zaynen shoyn aroysgemarshirt, un mir zoln do in shtot nit blaybn.

310
00:19:44,738 --> 00:19:47,752
keyn daytshn iz shoyn nit geven; zey zaynen antlofn.

311
00:19:47,961 --> 00:19:49,372
nu,

312
00:19:50,500 --> 00:19:53,017
zogt er, "oyf morgn in der fri...

313
00:19:53,260 --> 00:19:58,901
m'hot geheysn mir," zogt er, "haynt aroysmarshirn, nor s'iz shoyn fintster un shpet.

314
00:19:58,901 --> 00:20:01,061
mir'n geyn morgn in der fri.

315
00:20:01,061 --> 00:20:06,724
nor greyt tsu ale produktn vos s'iz do: fleysh, alts, kokht oys,

316
00:20:06,724 --> 00:20:09,459
un mir'n mitnemen oyfn DOROGe

317
00:20:09,459 --> 00:20:12,310
oysgekokhte esn." azoy hobn zey geton in,

318
00:20:12,310 --> 00:20:13,655
NA KUKHNE. zey hobn...

319
00:20:14,686 --> 00:20:17,103
az ir hot gegrobn di erd,

320
00:20:17,103 --> 00:20:19,643
v- in vos zayt ir geven ongeton?

321
00:20:19,643 --> 00:20:20,701
mit vos...?

322
00:20:19,764 --> 00:20:20,764
vi vi?

323
00:20:20,853 --> 00:20:27,597
az ir hot gegrobn di kanaves, mit vos zayn- z- zayt ir geven ongeton? vos hot ir getrogn oyf zikh?

324
00:20:26,620 --> 00:20:30,631
di zelbe zakhn. vos mir hobn gehat, dos hobn mir getrogn.

325
00:20:31,942 --> 00:20:35,816
mit vos hot men aykh gekormet? vu hot ir gelebt?

326
00:20:35,672 --> 00:20:37,908
zey hobn keyn zakh nit gekormet.

327
00:20:37,908 --> 00:20:40,351
⟨i-⟩ vos m'hot gegebn in lager,

328
00:20:40,965 --> 00:20:42,995
vos m'hot oysgekokht.

329
00:20:42,995 --> 00:20:48,266
in der fri flegt men oystrinken a gloz kave. me fleg gebn a shtikl broyt.

330
00:20:48,981 --> 00:20:52,333
di broyt iz geven ot aza shtikl.

331
00:20:52,491 --> 00:20:53,632
ver s'hot

332
00:20:53,740 --> 00:20:59,000
oyfgegesn di gantse oyf eyn mol, oyf frishtik, hot nit gehat oyf shpeter.

333
00:20:59,000 --> 00:21:02,827
nor ikh fleg tseshnaydn di broyt azoy oyf dray teyln:

334
00:21:02,827 --> 00:21:06,559
oyf in der fri a shtikele, oyf bay tog, oyf in ovnt.

335
00:21:07,898 --> 00:21:13,444
fleg ikh oystrinken in der fri di kave mit a shtikele broyt, un avek⟨geyn⟩ arbetn.

336
00:21:13,838 --> 00:21:19,519
az mir flegn kumen, flegt men gebn a teler zup, fleg ikh hobn nokh a shtikele broyt.

337
00:21:20,301 --> 00:21:27,045
un bay nakht flegt men gebn kave. fleg ikh oyfesn di drite shtikl broyt. azoy hob ikh ayngeteylt

338
00:21:27,118 --> 00:21:28,338
ale tog

339
00:21:28,338 --> 00:21:30,769
oyf dray mol di shtikele broyt.

340
00:21:30,769 --> 00:21:34,234
nor froyen hobn nit gekent oyshaltn;

341
00:21:34,375 --> 00:21:37,845
zey flegn oyfesn oyf eyn mol di gantse broyt.

342
00:21:38,121 --> 00:21:42,232
un nokh dem flegn zey veln esn. vos flegn zey ton?

343
00:21:42,525 --> 00:21:44,156
⟨a,⟩ bay der arbet

344
00:21:44,297 --> 00:21:47,620
iz geven gertn, gertner.

345
00:21:47,620 --> 00:21:50,568
flegn zey geyn ganvenen merelekh,

346
00:21:50,676 --> 00:21:51,972
kroyt,

347
00:21:51,972 --> 00:21:53,319
bulves.

348
00:21:53,612 --> 00:21:57,436
nor me fleg zey azoy fil hargenen az me fleg zey khapn.

349
00:21:57,612 --> 00:21:59,979
ikh bin keyn mol nit gegangen

350
00:21:59,979 --> 00:22:01,781
oyf di felder

351
00:22:01,781 --> 00:22:03,069
ganvenen.

352
00:22:03,069 --> 00:22:06,696
vos ikh hob gehat, vos m'hot gegebn in lager, dos hob ikh gegesn,

353
00:22:06,696 --> 00:22:07,883
un VSЁ.

354
00:22:08,252 --> 00:22:12,118
vayl az zey flegn gebn a hak ibern kop flegt men blaybn lign.

355
00:22:14,308 --> 00:22:16,505
ir hot gehat khavertes?

356
00:22:17,967 --> 00:22:18,967
oy.

357
00:22:21,321 --> 00:22:23,745
zey zaynen nit geven mit mir,

358
00:22:24,072 --> 00:22:26,346
nit in geto, nit in lager,

359
00:22:26,346 --> 00:22:27,001
neyn.

360
00:22:28,189 --> 00:22:34,629
ver s'iz geven aroysgeforn in Rusland, ver s'iz geven antlofn, ver aher, ahin.

361
00:22:35,344 --> 00:22:37,380
ikh hob zey keynem nit gezen.

362
00:22:37,605 --> 00:22:41,294
nu, ⟨ikh⟩ volt dertseyln nokh, volt dertseyln nokh.

363
00:22:43,849 --> 00:22:48,850
un dortn hot ir gehat tsevishn, vi ir hot gegrobn di kanaves,

364
00:22:48,858 --> 00:22:55,161
hot ir gehat khavertes velkhe nit iz? efsher dermont ir zikh vegn vemen nit iz, dertseylt ir.

365
00:22:55,168 --> 00:22:58,275
vu iz geven ayer man ot o di tsayt?

366
00:23:00,707 --> 00:23:05,105
mayn man iz geven, di mener hot men avekgeshikt in, DACHAU.

367
00:23:07,255 --> 00:23:08,548
in DACHAU.

368
00:23:09,330 --> 00:23:10,809
dortn

369
00:23:11,271 --> 00:23:13,610
iz geven a epidemye,

370
00:23:14,038 --> 00:23:17,154
⟨a⟩ epidemye, un er iz oykh krank gevorn.

371
00:23:17,447 --> 00:23:19,005
un er iz geshtorbn.

372
00:23:19,005 --> 00:23:20,799
er iz geshtorbn in lager.

373
00:23:21,312 --> 00:23:25,214
azoy hot men mir gezogt. s'iz geven gekumen

374
00:23:25,214 --> 00:23:27,246
eyner fun lager,

375
00:23:29,125 --> 00:23:32,560
vi hot men im gerufn? ⟨takesh neyn⟩...

376
00:23:33,037 --> 00:23:36,020
Sh- Shloyme Shneyder.

377
00:23:36,415 --> 00:23:38,164
hot er dertseylt

378
00:23:39,013 --> 00:23:42,331
az er hot gezen mayn man farn toyt.

379
00:23:42,490 --> 00:23:44,138
er hot gezogt...

380
00:23:44,650 --> 00:23:47,934
er hot gehat bilder fun mir. hot er gezogt tsu im,

381
00:23:47,934 --> 00:23:52,221
"nem tsu di bilder, vestu ir opgebn az du vest ir trefn."

382
00:23:52,243 --> 00:23:57,873
hot er gezogt, "vos zol ikh nemen di bilder az ikh veys nit tsu ikh'l blaybn lebn?"

383
00:23:58,825 --> 00:24:02,177
hot er nit genumen. nor dos hot er mir dertseylt,

384
00:24:02,436 --> 00:24:04,685
az er iz geven krank oyf,

385
00:24:04,685 --> 00:24:06,168
oyf a tif...

386
00:24:06,300 --> 00:24:10,563
s'iz geven a epidemye, un er iz geshtorbn dortn, in lager.

387
00:24:13,084 --> 00:24:14,411
nu...

388
00:24:16,999 --> 00:24:18,714
nokh dem...

389
00:24:19,750 --> 00:24:21,467
vos iz geven nokh dem?

390
00:24:24,289 --> 00:24:27,472
nu, nokh dem iz avek a bisl tsayt,

391
00:24:28,339 --> 00:24:30,596
un di krig hot zikh geendikt.

392
00:24:32,701 --> 00:24:41,368
dertseylt mir, efsher iz geven bay aykh, ver nit iz gedenkt ir fun di vos hobn gegrobn bay aykh di kanaves mit aykh, in Shtutgof?

393
00:24:41,315 --> 00:24:42,553
vi, vi zogt ir?

394
00:24:42,631 --> 00:24:48,652
 e- efsher veyst ir, gedenkt ir khavertes velkhe hot, hobn gegro- di froyen,

395
00:24:48,652 --> 00:24:52,315
velkhe hobn gegrobn di kanaves mit aykh?

396
00:24:56,959 --> 00:25:00,142
eyne, lebt zi itster in Poyln.

397
00:25:01,482 --> 00:25:03,467
mir zaynen geven shkheynim.

398
00:25:04,688 --> 00:25:10,166
zi hot oykh in eyn un fertsikstn yor geborn a yingele; m'hot oykh tsugenumen oyf di aktsye.

399
00:25:11,202 --> 00:25:14,638
nu, un zaynen mir geven tsuzamen in Shtuthof.

400
00:25:15,117 --> 00:25:18,874
zi hot oykh geven bay di, gegrobn di kanaln.

401
00:25:20,938 --> 00:25:25,522
nu, ver iz geven nokh? me ken gedenken, ver s'iz nokh geven?

402
00:25:32,174 --> 00:25:36,877
s'iz geven faln az men flegt helfn eyner dem tsveytn?

403
00:25:36,736 --> 00:25:37,684
helfn?

404
00:25:37,350 --> 00:25:38,157
ye.

405
00:25:37,850 --> 00:25:39,698
s'iz nit geven mit vos tsu helfn.

406
00:25:40,328 --> 00:25:41,925
nit geven mit vos.

407
00:25:42,775 --> 00:25:45,097
m'hot zikh aleyn nit gekent helfn.

408
00:25:46,015 --> 00:25:48,045
m'iz gelebt fun dos,

409
00:25:48,045 --> 00:25:50,463
fun RATSION vos zey hobn gegebn.

410
00:25:50,942 --> 00:25:55,239
ver s'hot oyfgegesn mit eyn mol, ver s'hot tseteylt zikh oyf dray mol,

411
00:25:55,650 --> 00:25:59,839
un azoy hot men gelebt. ver s'fleg geyn oyf di felder ganvenen.

412
00:25:59,839 --> 00:26:04,911
zey flegn kumen ⟨a-⟩ UNK flegn zey, nakher, az zey flegn onganvenen bulves,

413
00:26:04,911 --> 00:26:11,270
flegn zey oyf di f- oyfn feld bay der arbet nakher makhn a fayer un opkokhn un dos esn.

414
00:26:11,513 --> 00:26:14,764
s'iz geven mentshn mit groyse apetitn.

